---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="千忆知答 — 知识库问答产品 | 千忆 AI"
  description="千忆知答是千忆 AI 工作室的知识库问答产品，将制度文档、FAQ、培训资料整理成可提问、可追溯来源的智能知识库。"
>
  <!-- ═══ Nav ═══ -->
  <header class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="logo"><span class="logo-mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>千忆 AI</a>
      <button class="nav-toggle" id="nav-toggle" aria-label="菜单" aria-expanded="false"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
      <nav class="nav-links" id="nav-menu">
        <a href="#problems">解决的问题</a>
        <a href="#how">怎么用</a>
        <a href="#faq">常见问题</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">预约演示</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- ═══ 1. Hero ═══ -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <h1>千忆知答，让企业资料变成<em>可追溯的答案</em></h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">把制度文档、产品手册、客服 FAQ、培训资料整理成可提问的知识库，让团队成员快速获得带来源的可靠答案。</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">加微信预约演示</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-ghost">申请体验版本</a>
          </div>
          <p class="hero-note">资料准备完整后，可快速搭建体验版本</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="product-mock">
            <div class="mock-toolbar"><span class="mock-dot"></span><span class="mock-dot"></span><span class="mock-dot"></span><span class="mock-title">千忆知答</span></div>
            <div class="mock-body">
              <div class="mock-search">员工手册中关于年假的规定是什么？</div>
              <div class="mock-result">
                <p class="mock-ans">根据《员工手册》第三章第 2.4 条：员工入职满一年享有 <strong>5 个工作日</strong> 带薪年假……</p>
                <div class="mock-sources"><span class="source-tag">员工手册 v3.2 · 第三章</span><span class="source-tag">考勤制度 v2.1 · 第五条</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mock-note">界面示意，后续替换为真实截图</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 2. Problems ═══ -->
    <section class="problems" id="problems" aria-labelledby="problems-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="problems-heading">它主要解决这三类问题</h2>
        <div class="problems-row">
          <div class="prob">
            <h3>资料分散</h3>
            <p>文档散在共享盘、邮件附件、聊天记录里，每次找资料都像翻箱倒柜。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="prob">
            <h3>版本混乱</h3>
            <p>制度改了、产品更新了，旧版本还在各个角落，新旧混在一起没人说得清。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="prob">
            <h3>答案无源</h3>
            <p>老员工离职带走了"谁知道"，新员工只能靠打听——答案有，但找不到源头。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 3. How + Scenarios ═══ -->
    <section class="how-section" id="how" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="how-heading">从资料到答案，很简单</h2>
        <div class="how-grid">
          <div class="how-steps">
            <div class="hs-item"><span class="hs-num">1</span><strong>上传资料</strong><span>支持 PDF、Word、Markdown、TXT 等常见格式，可批量导入已有文档库。</span></div>
            <div class="hs-item"><span class="hs-num">2</span><strong>直接提问</strong><span>像问同事一样用日常语言提问，一次提问同时检索所有关联文档。</span></div>
            <div class="hs-item"><span class="hs-num">3</span><strong>查看来源</strong><span>每条回答标注文档名称和章节位置，点击即可跳转到原文核对。</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="how-scenarios">
            <p class="hs-label">适合这些场景</p>
            <ul>
              <li>企业制度查询</li>
              <li>产品手册问答</li>
              <li>客服 FAQ</li>
              <li>新人培训</li>
              <li>售后知识库</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 3.5 Trust ═══ -->
    <section class="trust-section" aria-labelledby="trust-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="trust-heading">专注知识库问答的工作室</h2>
        <div class="trust-grid">
          <div class="trust-point">
            <h4>聚焦一个方向</h4>
            <p>只做知识库问答这一件事，不做通用 chatbot、不做大而全的平台。你的资料整理和问答效果是我们唯一关心的交付质量。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-point">
            <h4>一对一交付</h4>
            <p>每个项目由团队直接对接，从资料评估到体验版本搭建全程跟进。不需要自己看文档、学配置、调参数。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-point">
            <h4>先试用，再决定</h4>
            <p>资料准备好之后先搭建体验版本，你和团队实际用起来觉得合适了，再讨论后续。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 4. FAQ ═══ -->
    <section class="faq-section" id="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
      <div class="container container-sm">
        <h2 id="faq-heading">常见问题</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details class="faq-item"><summary>支持哪些文档格式？</summary><p>支持 PDF、Word、Markdown、HTML、TXT 等常见格式，可从本地上传。后续可扩展对接飞书文档、Confluence 等知识源。</p></details>
          <details class="faq-item"><summary>回答会显示来源吗？</summary><p>会。每条回答都附有来源引用，包括文档名称和章节位置，点击可跳转到原文核对。</p></details>
          <details class="faq-item"><summary>是否支持私有化部署？</summary><p>支持。可部署到私有云或本地服务器，满足对数据安全有更高要求的团队。</p></details>
          <details class="faq-item"><summary>如何预约演示？</summary><p>添加微信 qianyi-ai，备注「千忆演示」，或填写下方表单提交预约信息。</p></details>
          <details class="faq-item"><summary>搭建体验版本需要多长时间？</summary><p>资料准备完整的情况下，通常 1-2 个工作日即可搭建出可试用的体验版本。具体时间取决于资料的规模和格式复杂度。</p></details>
          <details class="faq-item"><summary>上传的资料安全吗？</summary><p>资料存储在你指定的环境中（本地服务器或私有云），不会用于模型训练。也支持私有化部署，数据完全不出你的网络。</p></details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 5. Contact ═══ -->
    <section class="contact-section" id="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
      <div class="container container-sm">
        <h2 id="contact-heading">想看看你的资料能不能做成知识库？</h2>
        <p class="contact-desc">可以先简单沟通资料类型和使用场景，再判断是否适合搭建体验版本。</p>
        <div class="contact-grid">
          <div class="contact-wechat">
            <span class="cw-label">微信</span>
            <span class="cw-value">qianyi-ai</span>
            <span class="cw-hint">添加时备注「千忆演示」</span>
          </div>
          <form class="contact-form" id="contact-form">
            <div class="form-row"><label for="name">称呼 <span class="label-req" aria-label="必填">*</span></label><input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="您的称呼" required autocomplete="name" /></div>
            <div class="form-row"><label for="team">团队 / 工作室 <span class="label-req" aria-label="必填">*</span></label><input type="text" id="team" name="team" placeholder="团队或工作室名称" required autocomplete="organization" /></div>
            <div class="form-row"><label for="contact-info">联系方式 <span class="label-req" aria-label="必填">*</span></label><input type="text" id="contact-info" name="contact" placeholder="微信、邮箱或手机号" required autocomplete="email" /></div>
            <div class="form-row"><label for="message">需求说明 <span class="label-opt">选填</span></label><textarea id="message" name="message" rows="2" placeholder="简单描述团队规模和使用场景"></textarea></div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">提交预约</button>
	            <p class="form-trust">提交后通常 24 小时内通过微信回复，你的信息仅用于沟通演示安排，不会用于其他用途。</p>
            <div class="form-success" id="form-success" hidden><p>已收到预约信息，也可以直接<strong>添加微信 <span class="wx-hl">qianyi-ai</span></strong> 沟通。</p></div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- ═══ Footer ═══ -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-brand"><strong>千忆 AI</strong><span>个人工作室品牌，专注于 AI 知识库与文档问答工具</span></div>
      <nav class="footer-links"><a href="#problems">解决的问题</a><a href="#how">怎么用</a><a href="#faq">常见问题</a><a href="#contact">联系与试用</a></nav>
      <div class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 千忆 AI</div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ═══ Shared ═══ */
  .container { max-width: 1160px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--space-8); }
  .container-sm { max-width: 680px; }
  h2 { font-size: var(--text-h2); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--color-ink); text-align: center; }

  /* ═══ Nav ═══ */
  .nav { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: var(--z-sticky); background: oklch(0.130 0.003 155 / 0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .nav-inner { max-width: 1160px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--space-8); height: 52px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
  .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2); text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-ink); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .logo-mark { width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 4px; background: var(--color-primary); }
  .nav-toggle { display: none; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2.5rem; font-size: var(--text-small); }
  .nav-links > a:not(.btn) { color: var(--color-ink); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
  .nav-links > a:not(.btn):hover { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: none; }

  /* ═══ Buttons ═══ */
  .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--text-small); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 0 var(--space-6); height: 44px; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; transition: background 150ms ease, border-color 150ms ease, transform 150ms ease; }
  .btn:hover { text-decoration: none; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--color-primary); color: var(--color-primary-text); }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--color-primary-hover); color: var(--color-primary-text); }
  .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--color-ink); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--color-primary); color: var(--color-primary); }
  .btn-sm { height: 34px; padding: 0 var(--space-4); font-size: var(--text-xs); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); }
  .btn-full { width: 100%; }

  /* ═══ 1. Hero ═══ */
  .hero { padding: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) 0 var(--space-12); }
  .hero-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem); align-items: center; }
  .hero-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-5); }
  .hero-text h1 { font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 3.5vw, 2.45rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.35; color: var(--color-ink); }
  .hero-text h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 50ch; }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-4); }
  .hero-note { font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--color-muted); }
  @keyframes heroIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  .hero-text h1, .hero-sub, .hero-actions, .hero-note { animation: heroIn 400ms ease-out both; }
  .hero-sub { animation-delay: 100ms; }
  .hero-actions { animation-delay: 200ms; }
  .hero-note { animation-delay: 300ms; }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .hero-text h1, .hero-sub, .hero-actions, .hero-note { animation: none; } }

  .hero-visual { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2); }
  .product-mock { width: 100%; max-width: 500px; background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); box-shadow: 0 1px 2px oklch(0 0 0 / 0.15), 0 4px 20px oklch(0 0 0 / 0.25); overflow: hidden; }
  .mock-toolbar { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3); background: oklch(0.145 0.002 155); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .mock-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .mock-dot:nth-child(1) { background: oklch(0.72 0.18 25); }
  .mock-dot:nth-child(2) { background: oklch(0.80 0.14 95); }
  .mock-dot:nth-child(3) { background: oklch(0.62 0.16 150); }
  .mock-title { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-muted); margin-left: var(--space-2); font-weight: 500; }
  .mock-body { padding: var(--space-3); }
  .mock-search { padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3); background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); }
  .mock-result { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-2); }
  .mock-ans { font-size: var(--text-small); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--color-ink); max-width: none; }
  .mock-sources { display: flex; gap: var(--space-2); flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .source-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: var(--text-xs); font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent-text); background: var(--color-accent); padding: 1px var(--space-2); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); transition: transform 150ms ease, box-shadow 150ms ease; }
  .source-tag:hover { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 12px oklch(0.660 0.150 60 / 0.35); }
  .mock-note { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-muted); }

  /* ═══ 2. Problems ═══ */
  .problems { padding: 0 0 var(--section-pad); }
  .problems h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-8); }
  .problems-row { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: var(--space-6); max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .prob { flex: 1; max-width: 280px; padding: var(--space-6); background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); }
  .prob h3 { font-size: var(--text-body); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  .prob p { font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ═══ 3. How + Scenarios ═══ */
  .how-section { padding: var(--section-pad) 0; background: var(--color-surface); }
  .how-section h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-10); }
  .how-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-10); align-items: start; max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .how-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3); }
  .hs-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-4); padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5); background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); animation: stepIn 400ms ease-out both; }
  .hs-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0ms; }
  .hs-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 100ms; }
  .hs-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 200ms; }
  @keyframes stepIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-8px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); } }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .hs-item { animation: none; } }
  .hs-num { width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-primary); color: var(--color-primary-text); font-size: var(--text-xs); font-weight: 700; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .hs-item strong { font-size: var(--text-small); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); white-space: nowrap; }
  .hs-item span { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-muted); }
  .how-scenarios { padding-top: var(--space-2); }
  .hs-label { font-size: var(--text-small); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-4); }
  .how-scenarios ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-2); }
  .how-scenarios li { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-ink); padding: 4px var(--space-3); background: oklch(0.660 0.150 60 / 0.10); border: 1px solid oklch(0.660 0.150 60 / 0.22); border-radius: var(--radius-full); }


  /* ═══ 3.5 Trust ═══ */
  .trust-section { padding: var(--section-pad) 0; background: var(--color-surface); text-align: center; }
  .trust-section h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-10); }
  .trust-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-8); max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left; }
  .trust-point { padding: var(--space-6); background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); }
  .trust-point h4 { font-size: var(--text-body); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  .trust-point p { font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ═══ 4. FAQ ═══ */
  .faq-section { padding: var(--section-pad) 0; }
  .faq-section h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-8); }
  .faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .faq-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .faq-item summary { list-style: none; padding: var(--space-4) 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--text-small); cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-4); color: var(--color-ink); user-select: none; }
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-item summary::after { content: '+'; flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-muted); width: 20px; text-align: center; }
  .faq-item[open] summary::after { content: '\2212'; }
  .faq-item summary:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
  @keyframes faqIn { from { opacity: 0; max-height: 0; padding-bottom: 0; } to { opacity: 1; max-height: 200px; padding-bottom: var(--space-4); } }
  .faq-item[open] > p { animation: faqIn 300ms ease-out both; overflow: hidden; }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .faq-item[open] > p { animation: none; } }
  .faq-item > p { padding: 0 0 var(--space-4); color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; font-size: var(--text-small); max-width: none; }

  /* ═══ 5. Contact ═══ */
  .contact-section { padding: var(--section-pad) 0; background: var(--color-surface); text-align: center; }
  .contact-section h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-3); }
  .contact-desc { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: var(--space-8); }
  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr; gap: var(--space-10); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left; }
  .contact-wechat { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-1); padding: var(--space-4); background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); height: fit-content; }
  .cw-label { font-size: var(--text-xs); font-weight: 600; color: oklch(0.720 0.140 60); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .cw-value { font-size: var(--text-body); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); }
  .cw-hint { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-muted); }

  .contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3); }
  .form-row { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-1); }
  .form-row label { font-size: var(--text-small); font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-ink); }
  .label-opt { font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-muted); }
  .label-req { color: var(--color-error); font-weight: 400; }
  .form-row input, .form-row textarea { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: var(--text-small); padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); background: var(--color-bg); color: var(--color-ink); transition: border-color 150ms ease; line-height: 1.5; }
  .form-row input:focus, .form-row textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--color-primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px oklch(0.620 0.160 150 / 0.20); }
  .form-row ::placeholder { color: oklch(0.450 0.005 155); }
  .form-success { padding: var(--space-4); background: oklch(0.660 0.150 60 / 0.08); border: 1px solid var(--color-accent); border-radius: var(--radius-md); font-size: var(--text-small); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--color-ink); text-align: center; }
  .form-success p { max-width: none; }
  .form-trust { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-muted); text-align: center; line-height: 1.5; max-width: none; }
  .wx-hl { font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-accent); }

  /* ═══ Footer ═══ */
  .footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: var(--space-5) 0; font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--color-muted); }
  .footer-inner { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-4); }
  .footer-brand { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .footer-brand strong { font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); font-size: var(--text-body); }
  .footer-brand span { font-size: var(--text-xs); }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: var(--space-5); }
  .footer-links a { color: var(--color-muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: var(--text-xs); }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--color-ink); text-decoration: none; }
  .footer-copy { width: 100%; padding-top: var(--space-3); margin-top: var(--space-3); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: var(--text-xs); }

  /* ═══ Responsive ═══ */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-text h1 { font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 4vw, 1.9rem); }
    .how-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-8); }
    .problems-row { gap: var(--space-4); flex-wrap: wrap; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-8); }
    /* hero-visual order removed: headline stays first on mobile */
    .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; }
    .hero-actions .btn { width: 100%; }
    .problems-row { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
    .prob { max-width: none; }
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 5vw, 1.65rem); }

    .nav-toggle { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: var(--space-2); }
    .nav-toggle span { display: block; width: 20px; height: 2px; background: var(--color-ink); border-radius: 1px; transition: transform 200ms ease, opacity 200ms ease; }
    .nav-toggle[aria-expanded="true"] span:nth-child(1) { transform: translateY(7px) rotate(45deg); }
    .nav-toggle[aria-expanded="true"] span:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0; }
    .nav-toggle[aria-expanded="true"] span:nth-child(3) { transform: translateY(-7px) rotate(-45deg); }
    .nav-links { display: none; position: absolute; top: 52px; left: 0; right: 0; background: var(--color-bg); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); flex-direction: column; padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-8); gap: var(--space-4); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px oklch(0 0 0 / 0.35); }
    .nav-links.open { display: flex; }
    .nav-links > a:not(.btn) { font-size: var(--text-body); }
    .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .footer-links { justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  (function() {
    var t = document.getElementById('nav-toggle');
    var m = document.getElementById('nav-menu');
    t && t.addEventListener('click', function() { var o = m.classList.toggle('open'); t.setAttribute('aria-expanded', o); });
    m && m.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(function(a) { a.addEventListener('click', function() { m.classList.remove('open'); t.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false'); }); });
    var f = document.getElementById("contact-form");
    f && f.addEventListener("submit", function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      var btn = f.querySelector("button[type="submit"]");
      btn.textContent = "提交中...";
      btn.disabled = true;
      setTimeout(function() {
        f.querySelectorAll(".form-row").forEach(function(r) { r.style.display = "none"; });
        btn.style.display = "none";
        f.querySelector(".form-trust").style.display = "none";
        document.getElementById("form-success").hidden = false;
      }, 800);
    });
  })();
</script>
